sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant API
  participant Session
  participant carts as carts
  participant mi as menu_items
  participant rest as restaurants
  participant dz as delivery_zones
  participant orders as orders
  participant CS as ChangeStream

  User->>API: POST /orders cartId deliveryAddress paymentMethod
  API->>Session: startTransaction

  API->>carts: findOne cartId userId
  Note over API: 1. Validar carrito existe

  API->>mi: find _id $in itemIds available true
  Note over API: 2. Items disponibles? Si no ABORT

  API->>rest: findOne restaurantId isAcceptingOrders true
  Note over API: 3. Restaurante abierto? Si no ABORT

  API->>dz: findOne restaurantId area $geoIntersects deliveryPoint
  Note over API: 4. En cobertura? Obtener deliveryFee. Si no ABORT

  API->>API: 5. Calcular total = subtotal + tax + deliveryFee

  API->>orders: insertOne status pending items snapshot statusHistory
  API->>mi: updateMany $inc salesCount per item
  API->>carts: deleteOne cartId

  API->>Session: commitTransaction

  Note over orders, CS: Propagacion asincrona
  orders->>CS: insert detectado
  CS->>CS: insert order_events toStatus pending
  CS->>CS: update restaurant_stats $inc totalOrders

  API-->>User: orderId orderNumber status pending
